{
  "stem": "7684.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And had an aunt and uncle-- it was a doctor's family-- that lived also in Apeldoorn, and I could visit them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was better for me, too, to get away from that small house, where my mother was sitting the whole day.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My one brother had a girlfriend, and I think they were-- in between-- were married.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My brother married.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so we were sitting-- and I thought it was very stuffy-- knitting the whole day-- and I just-- I was 19, and I went out and went to a family and helped them.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one day, I was standing outside.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the same street was a very large house, and a Catholic priest there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that all that I really remember things like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then this Catholic priest came to me and said, how do you think that you can be safe-- that you won't be sent away, out of the country?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- I don't know how I came up with the idea say to him that the only way that a not-Jewish people take me in and, uh-- and that-- I am not there anymore-- I have nothing to do with the family.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I'm out of there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the same afternoon, he came-- or a day later-- I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know he came to me, and he say, I have a family-- I know found somebody what will take you in.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did you know this priest before?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I looked Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really do-- in Holland, especially-- I have a big nose, and I was a little bit darker and talking with my hands a little bit.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm a real, typical Jewish person.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not seen, perhaps, in America, but in Holland I was.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
